牙醫可唔可以做？牙醫專科又可唔可以做到？"},{"pid":"d2ae66e771d95ad637f40c0ebeaba38c12fa1d02","tid":1425563,"uid":155707,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"444e525f759b0f5c7a7f18e8535e2d300ce4dc52","tid":1425563,"uid":73462,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9dae5b2e720b08fc0d30d1c903adf048ea6b96d4","tid":1425563,"uid":155707,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"7d7bfa2808343a0d3a0397df990c19bd329df975","tid":1425563,"uid":73462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:53:06.000Z","msg":"訓唔著覺開post 求屌醒<br />\n呢兩三日就要決定 過左就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:55:56.000Z","msg":"年輕時應該要衝動啲<br />\n想做就應該去做<br />\n唔好俾自己有後悔嘅機會<br />\n呢一刻可能覺得好難揀<br />\n但唔好係最可以拼搏嘅時候<br />\n揀最舒適嘅選擇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:58:35.000Z","msg":"其實最大壓力會係睇住同期同學成家立室 有車有樓 自己仲on99 咁讀緊死書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:02:48.000Z","msg":"每個人行嘅路好唔同<br />\n有人好似你宜家咁大個<br />\n目標就只係想成家立室<br />\n最緊要係你自己心態<br />\n從來可以懷疑自己嘅<br />\n都只可以得你自己一個<br />\n<br />\n去到你呢個年紀仲可以揀讀書<br />\n其實都係一件幸福嘅事<br />\n追夢從來唔容易<br />\n若果可以輕易達成嘅<br />\n仲係唔係你嘅夢？"},{"pid":"d5e9d60dee51c2c93a00fbef0c4f68d6fe250ef6","tid":1425563,"uid":7030,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:05:26.000Z","msg":"救唔番香港做乜都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"d715fac2918e3542ca1164a0451c583d5a4913e4","tid":1425563,"uid":156144,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:10:36.000Z","msg":"過咗30歲你就會冇咗團火 亦冇得再選擇 不如趁而家後生闖蕩一下 支持你讀medic"},{"pid":"1a377f7413f8c7c4fc8d01ad61ae035563e15685","tid":1425563,"uid":5480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:14:13.000Z","msg":"本身係牙醫再讀mbbs可以更加專<br />\n香港唔係好多個 搵得仲多錢"},{"pid":"18ced255c5ad7f8facaa3ed2e7b675b6958b5628","tid":1425563,"uid":207259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:17:13.000Z","msg":"投錯咗 想正皮㩒咗負皮<br />\n既然醫生係兒時夢想 又係正當職業就不妨試吓啦<br />\n25歲又唔係老 有咩好顧慮呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b104a46e36a5d0a1f41944d13caa6fa242ddd8fa","tid":1425563,"uid":167937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:21:53.000Z","msg":"讀完medic如果有咩事<br />\n可唔可以做返牙醫？<br />\n有就medic啦<br />\n無論點都好，希望將來你用你專業惠澤社群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9578efdd0cba887b440e31223b880dd7c5a9a70d","tid":1425563,"uid":241865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:11:29.000Z","msg":"既然初心係想做西醫 趁年輕試下 反正衰左都做得返牙醫<br />\n<br />\n試過唔得起碼叫試過<br />\n無試過將來係有車有樓但內心唔滿足<br />\n<br />\n我都係30個陣豁出去辭工創業<br />\n雖然放棄人人都想嘅職業 依家都好辛苦<br />\n但我依家內心好滿足<br />\n<br />\n共勉之！"},{"pid":"a3b0bf5b03ff27630c8f993bc55ac0b6a4ac5b82","tid":1425563,"uid":13414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:18:38.000Z","msg":"踏出comfort zone <br />\nStudy medic"},{"pid":"a83c6b50c3510eeabf0fe9b88ef9dd2d145afe03","tid":1425563,"uid":46340,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:24:52.000Z","msg":"牙醫都要出去搵人箍牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（箍牙jj) 岑儉箍牙如何？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/902209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/902209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d35d43076bd83d32a418dd139878fe8cb5daba1e","tid":1425563,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:14:54.000Z","msg":"牙醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫人整番好棚牙何嘗唔係一件壯舉"},{"pid":"2fa697ae0126eddfe192836e95c59e7aef676c03","tid":1425563,"uid":75959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:52:10.000Z","msg":"MBBS 就去啦，不過你係咪驚讀緊無收入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />